LKinfo                  Specifying the Lattice Krig covariance
                        object('LKinfo') and related utility functions.
LKrig                   Spatial prediction and inference using a
                        compactly supported multi-resolution basis and
                        a lattice model for the basis coefficients.
LKrig.MLE               Simple function to search over covariance
                        parameters for Lattice Krig
LKrig.basis             Functions for generating a multiresolution,
                        compactly supported basis, multiresolution
                        covariance functions and simulating from these
                        processes.
LKrig.coef              Internal functions for LatticeKrig package.
LKrig.rowshift.periodic
                        Miscellaneous internal functions for
                        LatticeKrig package.
LKrig.sim               Functions for simulating a multiresolution
                        process following the Lattice Krig covariance
                        model.
LKrigDefaultFixedFunction
                        Creates fixed part of spatial model.
LatticeKrig             User-friendly spatial prediction and inference
                        using a compactly supported multi-resolution
                        basis and a lattice model for the basis
                        coefficients.
Radial.basis            Two dimensional radial basis functions based on
                        a Wendland function.
